      <bioghist id="aspace_3b05319208c28cad3c02d8bf4dff0d0b">
         <head>Evelyn Hardy</head>
         <p>Evelyn Hardy was born on February 13, 1902 Gregory, Alyse (married)- many letters are about her after her death. letters to Evelyn Hardy after Alyse Gregory's death and relating to Evelyn Hardy's article on her life and character.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_4b88d1e7a738087a3860b547e14fea2c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Evelyn Hardy Papers contains correspondence with various individuals and drafts of poems by Hardy. The bulk of the correspondence is with Alyse Gregory. The papers span 1950-1974.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
